name: Dish Out
description: When hit by a Brute Attack, user strikes back with 2x power.

name: Haymaker
description: If it misses, the user loses half their HP.

name: Gambler
description: If it misses, the user loses half their HP.

name: Slug
description: The slower the opponent, the stronger the attack.

name: Uppercut
description: Inflicts damage equal to 15% of their total stats

name: Enlightmenment
description: Raises Sp. Def on first turn, attacks on second.

name: Crystalizer
description: User attacks for 2-3 turns but then becomes confused. Raises Sp. Atk

name: Polish
description: Recovers 10 hp, heals afflictions, and resets all stat changes.

name: Lights Out
description: Recovers 10 hp, heals afflictions, and resets all stat changes.

name: Packet Loss
description: User recovers half the HP inflicted on an afflicted opponent.

name: Defense Matrix
description: Halves damage from Special attacks for 5 turns.

name: Brute Force
description: Inflicts damage 25-50% of user's Special Attack.

name: Firewall
description: Halves damage from Physical attacks for 5 turns.

name: Regen
description: User is paralyzed for 2 turns, but fully healed.

name: Log Off
description: Allows User to tag in another Toshimon in same turn

name: Tunnel
description: Digs underground on first turn, attacks on second. Can also escape from caves.

name: Frack
description: Power is doubled if opponent is underground from using Dig.

name: Vanish
description: Disappears for one turn. Confuses opponent.

name: Ascension
description: Flies up on first turn, attacks on second turn.

name: Soulsuck
description: User recovers half the HP inflicted on opponent.

name: Haunt
description: Inflicts damage equal to 15% of the users total stats

name: Frighten
description: Charges on first turn, attacks on second. May cause flinching. High critical hit ratio.

name: Flame-nado
description: May trap opponent, damaging them for 4-5 turns.

name: Burnout
description: Hits twice if speed is lower than opponent.

name: Blaze It
description: User recovers half the HP inflicted on opponent.

name: Combust
description: Charges on first turn, attacks on second. High critical hit ratio.

name: Wrap
description: May trap opponent, damaging them for 4-5 turns.

name: Morph
description: Changes user's type to that of its first move.

name: Meditate
description: Raises user's Attack and Special Attack.

name: Lullaby
description: User rests, recovering 25% of max HP each turn it is asleep

name: Modulator
description: User performs almost any move in the game at random.

name: Mimic
description: User performs the opponent's last move.

name: Coach
description: Doubles XP for the duration of the battle

name: Medpack
description: User recovers half its max HP. Only useable once per deployment

name: Gain
description: User recovers half its max HP. Disabled for 3 turns.

name: Sleepwalker
description: Randomly uses any move if sleeping

name: Clone
description: Uses HP to creates a decoy that takes hits.

name: Throw
description: Always takes off half of the opponent's HP. Cooldown.

name: Carbon Copy
description: User takes on the form and attacks of the opponent.

name: Spinal Tap
description: May paralyze, burn or freeze opponent.

name: Shoo
description: In battles, the opponent switches. In the wild, the Toshimon runs.

name: Berate
description: May trap opponent, damaging them for 4-5 turns.

name: Heartbreak
description: Must be used 3 separate times. The total damage absorbed on the first two times is doubled and inflicted on the opponent on the third use.

name: Kissy Face
description: May lower opponent's Speed by one stage.

name: Takeaway
description: Opponent can't use its last attack for a few turns.

name: Warm Embrace
description: Raises user's Sp. Attack when hit.

name: Yawn
description: Puts opponent and user to sleep.

name: Ice Shield
description: User's stats cannot be changed for a period of time.

name: Grow
description: User recovers half the HP inflicted on opponent.

name: Mold Spore
description: Drains HP from opponent each turn.

name: Symbiote
description: User attacks for 2-3 turns but then becomes confused.

name: Overgrowth
description: Charges on first turn, attacks on second.

name: Poison
description: Poisons opponent. May lower opponent's Special Defense.

name: Whirlpool
description: May trap opponent, damaging them for 4-5 turns.

name: Bairzooka
description: A strong blast that also damages the user.

name: Liquidation
description: Powerful move with low accuracy. Hurts user when attack misses.

name: Supply Bomb
description: Throws a bomb at the enemy that also damages the user.

name: Wimpy Strike
description: A weak attack with low accuracy and high recoil that is only usable when every other move has 0 SP.
